---
title: Cheat's Beef Stroganoff with Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: We've adapted this Russian fave by adding soy sauce – it’s the secret ingredient that adds loads flavour to this dish while
shortening the normal cooking time! But you'll still find the key elements of mushrooms, beef strips and sour cream, plus a
creamy mash to soak up the sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheat-s-beef-stroganoff-2baf40e2.jpg
